      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i know i should talk to someone but it feels useless. like what would be the point? even if i talk, the \"person\" they are talking to is just the act. i'm just tired of the effort it takes to stay in this body and keep up the performance. it's so exhausting to pretend to exist when there's nothing actually there.",
